Channing “Stacks” Lorenzo and Troy “Two Dimes” Donovan trade hard-hitting blows with Legado del Fantasma in a battle for control. Catch WWE action on Peacock, WWE Network, FOX, USA Network, Sony India and more.
Katana Chance & Kayden Carter take flight to try and dethrone NXT Women’s Tag Team Champions Toxic Attraction. Catch WWE action on Peacock, WWE Network, FOX, USA Network, Sony India and more.
Trick Williams helps Carmelo Hayes gain the edge by tying Cameron Grimes' hand to the ropes. Catch WWE action on Peacock, WWE Network, FOX, USA Network, Sony India and more.
Wendy Choo fires up to level Mandy Rose after the NXT Women’s Champion tore apart her body pillow. Catch WWE action on Peacock, WWE Network, FOX, USA Network, Sony India and more.
Julius & Brutus Creed toss Pretty Deadly around the ring in pursuit of the NXT Tag Team Titles. Catch WWE action on Peacock, WWE Network, FOX, USA Network, Sony India and more.
Joe Gacy continues to play mind games with Bron Breakker in an attempt to force a disqualification from the NXT Champion. Catch WWE action on Peacock, WWE Network, FOX, USA Network, Sony India and more.

NXT Women's Tag Team Championship
Toxic Attraction (Gigi Dolin & Jacy Jayne) (c) defeat Katana Chance & Kayden Carter to retain the titles
NXT North American Championship
Carmelo Hayes defeats Cameron Grimes (c) to win the title
NXT Women's Championship
Mandy Rose (c) defeats Wendy Choo to retain the title
NXT Tag Team Championship
"If Creed Brothers lose they have to leave Diamond Mine"The Creed Brothers (Brutus & Julius Creed) defeat Pretty Deadly (Elton Prince & Kit Wilson) (c) to win the titles
NXT Championship
